              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Artistry covers the creation of visual and performing arts, like painting, sculpture, music, and dance. In a magical setting, it can entertain, inspire, or even weave spells through captivating performances. Skilled artists might conjure illusions, sway emotions, or encode secrets in their creations. This expertise shines for bards, enchanters, and heroes who wield creativity to overcome challenges or rally allies.",
